Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPresident Trump is joined in Aurora, Colorado by Cindy Romero, whose footage of Venezuelan gang members taking over her apartment complex went viral."You're very brave, Cindy... I promise you this: Kamala Harris' reign of terror ends the day I take the oath of office."
